 Retrospective insights captured after completing tracks, PR merges, and development milestones. Most recent entries at the top.
 
 ---
 
+## 2026-04-13 ‚Äî Phase 3 Fixes (Complete Site Redesign)
+
+### What Happened
+
+- Fixed Phase 3 incomplete tasks for reading-advantage and primary-advantage pages.
+- Replaced emoji icons (üßÝ ‚úçÔ∏è) in primary-advantage with Brain and PenTool Lucide equivalents.
+- Removed unused `showDecorations` prop from HeroSection interface and all 5 call sites.
+- Removed unused imports (CardHeader, CardTitle) from home page.
+- Fixed test mock to return `/images/placeholder.png` for i18n keys ending in `.image` (prevents Next/Image error on relative paths without leading `/`).
+- Fixed regex-based test assertions that matched multiple elements by using more specific queries.
+
+### Lessons
+
+- The `useScopedI18n` mock must return valid image paths for keys ending in `.image` ‚Äî otherwise Next/Image rejects them at render time.
+- Regex `/hero\./i` in `getByText` can match multiple elements when the mock returns strings containing the pattern ‚Äî use `getAllByRole` with count assertions instead.
+- `showDecorations` prop was declared in HeroProps but never used in the component body ‚Äî always check that props are actually consumed before shipping.
+- Build errors from unused vars must be fixed before push ‚Äî CI will reject.
+
+---
